# Sweet Life Café — environment variables
# Copy to .env.local and fill in. Never commit real values.
# The app runs without these set; email notifications are simply skipped.

# Resend API key — sends contact-form and sushi pre-order notification emails.
# Get one at https://resend.com. Optional for local UI work; required in
# production for enquiries to reach the café inbox (info@sweetlife.cafe).
RESEND_API_KEY=
